This is a showcases of the various types of graphic charts that are available in Joget Enterprise/Professional DX.
这是在中可用的各种类型的图形图表的展示。
Uses SQL query commands to retrieve and populate the chart.
使用SQL查询命令检索和填充图表。
You can define the height, width and color of the rendered chart.
可以定义呈现的图表的高度、宽度和颜色。
If you choose bar chart, you can specify to render in horizontal or vertical orientation.
如果选择柱状图，可以指定以水平或垂直方向呈现
In additional, bar charts allow you to display stack elements.
另外，柱状图允许显示堆栈元素。
All charts allow you to key in additional text above and below the chart. This app used the bottom footer to provide additional description about the chart.
所有的图表都允许你在图表上方和下方键入额外的文字。这个应用程序使用底部的页脚来提供关于图表的额外描述。
Finally, you decide the source of the data (Datasource) or database to 'pull' your data from. It can be an external database outside of Joget.
最后，您决定从数据的来源(数据源)或数据库“拉”数据。它可以是Joget之外的外部数据库。
The following are features of Joget Charts:
. To view the chart properties, edit the userview and hover over the chart menu until you see the properties link. Click on the properties link and study the respective chart properties tabs.

You can learn how the app generated the charts in
你可以学习如何在 用户视图生成图表。要查看图表属性，编辑用户视图并将鼠标悬停在图表菜单上，直到您看到属性链接。单击属性链接并研究相应的图表属性选项卡。

The following are features of Joget Charts:
Uses SQL query commands to retrieve and populate the chart. You can define the height, width and color of the rendered chart. If you choose bar chart, you can specify to render in horizontal or vertical orientation. In additional, bar charts allow you to display stack elements. All charts allow you to key in additional text above and below the chart. This app used the bottom footer to provide additional description about the chart. Finally, you decide the source of the data (Datasource) or database to 'pull' your data from. It can be an external database outside of Joget.

This showcase app features many of the low-code/no-code application development complete with workflow process.
这个展示应用程序的特点是许多低代码/无代码的应用程序开发完成的工作流程。

In the workflow example, a user can raise a request and submit to two approvers. The request form displays the use of multipage forms, a variety of form fields, spreadsheet and file/image upload fields. The app is complete with email notification. Approvers can approve the request, instruct the requester to resubmit the form or outright reject the form.

Login to proceed.
在工作流示例中，用户可以提出请求并提交给两个审批者。请求表单显示了多页表单、各种表单字段、电子表格和文件/图像上传字段的使用。该应用程序是完整的电子邮件通知。审批者可以批准请求，指示请求者重新提交表单或直接拒绝表单。 登录继续。
